{"tid":1635451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"代post: 給放學搭校巴嘅小朋友","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:22:45.000Z","uid":205289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d28fca931777a53a842692a45f000779fa3ddfc","tid":1635451,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"各位小朋友, 我明白大家返學上體育堂同美術堂，有好成<br />\n<br />\n績係好令人興奮嘅事，會好想向同學分享，但係請記得，<br />\n<br />\n喺校巴內保持安靜，唔好打擾司機專心揸車，咁樣會令全<br />\n<br />\n車同學仔有危險、仲要唔知車上邊係咪得同班同學/自己間<br />\n<br />\n學校校巴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔該搭得校巴、就直接返歸！唔好話怕麻煩人地，<br />\n<br />\n喺其他地方轉車，當全世都無公共交通工具、除咗校巴、<br />\n<br />\n就只有狗車，你想坐嗎？"},{"pid":"68e964abb73b4d00391233da922eff62b98bf259","tid":1635451,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"575974c565a05754d9893a0a4f9251e4d576a536","tid":1635451,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"我屌<br />\n你<br />\n個<br />\n老母 <br />\n打好啲<br />\n字<br />\n得唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d114c8262328a4fded4b52b8c75ac6dabbe48a77","tid":1635451,"uid":180168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"轉車係保護自己其中一個方法<br />\n就係因為佢地知家長車都未必信得過"},{"pid":"f40cf7dab912d64b06729fb914ab6801981c8315","tid":1635451,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"575974c565a05754d9893a0a4f9251e4d576a536","tid":1635451,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"我屌<br />\n你<br />\n個<br />\n老母 <br />\n打好啲<br />\n字<br />\n得唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:01:22.000Z","msg":"唔好意思囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b7e99e175d413ff3cf5ea98c65878a224d3777","tid":1635451,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"